        "title": "How exactly the line is getting printed on &quot;Console&quot; using System.out.print()",
        "body": "<p>If i want to print a line <\/p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>This is Java programming language<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>to the console using <code>System.out.print()<\/code>, which and how many process gets used to print this line, and how we can compare it with writing the same line to file using <code>FileWriter<\/code> or <code>BufferedWriter<\/code>. <\/p>\n",
